{"tid":1444014,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"洋蔥注意: 文宣/mv組 希望你地可以幫香港人打氣","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:36:40.000Z","uid":252096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"30e0213e349095291e5203ff4c825c5a1df6c5c3","tid":1444014,"uid":252096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nr1i5a37R74\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNr1i5a37R74&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqhmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=7c1eb7fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nr1i5a37R74</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">許廷鏗-面具 我係到送比各位為香港努力的巴絲</span><br />\n<br />\n不論你係前線 後援 急救 文宣 定係鍵戰 甚至捐款者 物資組 <br />\n總之你係有良知 關心香港 愛護香港的<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你 都值得成為依一首歌的一份子</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我認我眼淺 但依首聽親都好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n除咗要強調五大訴求 政府的多次謊言 警黑合作 無惡不作<br />\n各區的連儂牆都比大家提供一個平台去發泄自己所想 幫自己人打氣<br />\n但都只限於文字上<br />\n即使古代打仗 都會有軍樂隊 用黎提升士氣 到依家點解我地仲未有屬於自己的一首歌?<br />\n今日見到有位巴打有首原創歌 覺得唔錯的<br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442683/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442683/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n經歷咗咁多場的夢遊  由6月9日開始 <br />\n我地走上街頭 面對暴政 暴警 黑勢力 不斷的抹黑<br />\n家變 情變 更甚者有義士變成烈士 失去生命 葬送前途<br />\n抱歉我並唔係要散佈負面能量 但要如何維持依場抗爭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">士氣係好重要</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n係8月7日 我地係尖沙咀過左一個抗爭以黎最愉快的晚上<br />\n我地亦都約定 抗爭勝利後要回到金鍾煲底 放下所有面具同gear<br />\n狂歡一整日 乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n<br />\n我好希望各位巴絲 經過咁多日的抗爭,要學識Free Hong Kong <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">亦都要學識Free Yourself</span> <br />\n適當時 停下來 聽一首歌 畫一幅畫 等等 找回自己 <br />\n要告訴自己 你也是人 面具下的你依然會痛<br />\n休息後 我們再重新出發 緊記 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭路上 一個也不能再少</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n巴絲們 只勉之"},{"pid":"7d49ce4c4ec776a6d917ee7974eb7ad54fa1abcd","tid":1444014,"uid":252096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:08:54.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b70c9e06ce76389ca64b6ca1c7a3321e5a9f41","tid":1444014,"uid":252096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:15:59.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7f2b5e3653edfbce6abc56f857cbf27803c66c","tid":1444014,"uid":252096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">721</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535a9ab17fe584319e2d28a03f413936cdbde3a4","tid":1444014,"uid":252096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:36:40.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}